[[File:2008-03-15 Reporter in front of the CNN Center 2.jpg|thumb|225px|WSB-TV reporter Ross Cavitt in front of the [[CNN Center]] in the aftermath of the [[2008 Atlanta tornado outbreak|2008 Atlanta tornado]].]]

The ''Severe Weather Team 2'' weather staff includes chief meteorologist [[Glenn Burns]] ([[American Meteorological Society|AMS]] [[American Meteorological Society#Certified Broadcast Meteorologist (CBM) Seal|Certified Broadcast Meteorologist]] Seal of Approval; weeknights at 4, 6 and 11 p.m.)

