* [[Tom Brokaw]] - anchor/reporter (1965<U+2013>1966; retired ''[[NBC Nightly News]]'' anchor; began his journalism career at WSB-TV)
* [[Dale Cardwell]] - investigative reporter (1996<U+2013>2007; 2008 Democratic candidate for [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]] in the U.S. Senate, now has own consumer website called trustdale.com)<ref>[http://www.ajc.com/metro/content/shared-blogs/ajc/politicalinsider/entries/2007/06/02/cardwell_leaves_wsbtv_one_day.html]</ref>
